scene.message:
Yukino: We've come quite high{nl}
up. The finale's getting{nl}
close. We've got to psych{nl}
ourselves up again!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Uugh, I'm beeat~ Come{nl}
on! Isn't there an elevator{nl}
or something?!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Getting fine weapons{nl}
and armor is pointless if you{nl}
don't equip them — a waste of{nl}
a treasure.{waitkey}We must check now and then.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: We managed to avoid{nl}
falling asleep.{waitkey}Let's press on without{nl}
letting our guard down.{waitkey}{ret}
